name: هندسة أكثر تعقيدًا حسب المستويات
description:
Inspired by patterns from Samarra(Iraq), part of my studies on Islamic geometric patterns and what you can do with them in terms of eye pleasing motion. Mathematically these patterns are suited for many great discoveries, as our ancestors have already proven. But, have they revealed all the possibilities? 

created with Trapcode Echospace in After Effects on 19-12-19 | 1:1 | 800x800 | 300 frames | 30fps
